[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/advanced_forcing"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST's 2\D bid is a perfect example of NMF. 
It provides EAST with the opportunity to show either a 4-card \H suit, 
OR 3-card \S support.

In this hand EAST actually has both. When that happens, showing the \Hs is 
first priority.}

